General.Name: Adventa Bhd
General.Description: Adventa Berhad, an investment holding company, supply of healthcare and related products and services to hospitals, healthcare centers, and pharmacies in Malaysia, Sri Lanka, Indonesia, and internationally. The company distributes medical and healthcare equipment and appliances; and medical disposal products, including personal protective equipment. It also offers storage and warehousing; and online healthcare services. Adventa Berhad was incorporated in 2003 and is based in Petaling Jaya, Malaysia.
